\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 I wonder if I could start by asking you the date you were born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname date}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Month}{\xmlattrvalue 7}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Day}
{\xmlattrvalue 7}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Year}{\xmlattrvalue 1897}}}July 7}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 , 1897{\*\xmlclose}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Thorrington.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Could you describe to me the house that you were born in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 
Well, I'm afraid I couldn't, but I could give you an idea. That's what the call the old barracks, an old wooden house. They used to be what they call 
years before the old barracks. You know, they had them all in each village. Most old villages had what they call the old barracks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 I see, is that the same as the barracks tha}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12978248\charrsid1594022 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 's down St. Osyth way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No. This was an old wooden place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Have you any idea why they called it a barracks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, from what I can remember they used to have soldiers in these.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 What sort of rooms did it have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 I couldn't tell you. We moved from there just after we ... they took me from there in a ....\{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well really what I was after was the house where you were as a child, if you could describe that to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Oh, well, that was another wooden house with a brick building on the back of it. The front was all boarded, wooden boarded. There was }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022  bedrooms, front room, a living room and a kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 What was in the kitchen, could you describe to me what it consisted of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 There was a big oven when we used to bake bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And just an ordinary stove, and shelves all round it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Was the stove part of the oven or was it separate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No, the stove was separate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 With an open grate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And there were shelves?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes, all round, and a copper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And any tapped water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 How did you mother get the water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 From a well just outside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did she have to share that with other families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No, we were on our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you have any other houses }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 earby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes, one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Was it adjoining?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No, the gardens separated us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Where did the family eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, you see, mostly in the living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did that adjoin the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 How many of you were there in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 7}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 , and father and mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And where did you come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Last but one, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 6}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 th.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Would you mind telling me the order of the children and the spaces between them, just roughly speaking to get an idea of the household.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, my oldest sister, she's still alive, she's about 83. Then there's another sister, she's a few years younger, I couldn't 
say exactly. And there's an elder brother, he's ... I should think he's }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 10}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022  years older than me. And then there's another }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022  more sisters, Nell's 75, well, 76 I expect Nellie is, and Winnie 74; I'm 71, and me other brother's 66.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 You ranged 66 to 83.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, she might be a bit older than that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes, well, there's roughly about 17 years, you are sort of spread out over that period.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Could you tell me what your father's job was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 He worked on the railway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did he do that all his working life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Would you be able to tell me what other jobs he had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 He finished up roadman on the Council ... farm labouring ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No, not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 What was his first job when he first started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 What, his?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 You don't know whether he went into the railways straight from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 You think he did something else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 I think he done something else afore that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Have you any idea what he was earning when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 15/-, 16/- a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did your mother earn anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did she not do any work, even casual work, any field work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Do you think she didn't do that ... I'll put this differ
ently. Do you think she would have liked to have, if she hadn't had so many children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, I don't know, hardly any women went out working in them days, was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 
there?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No, a few people did a little casual ... picking up the potatoes and that so of t
hing, but there wasn't much, really, when you had children. What age were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 I expect I was between }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022  and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 .
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did all the children round about go at that age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Where was the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Thorrington.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 How far did you have to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Oh, not far, about half a mile.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And you walked, I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you go along with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you take food with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No, used to come home to dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And there were no school dinners then, were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No. No free milk or anything (laughter).
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Could you tell me what your mother used to cook for dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, vegetables, potatoes, greens, anything what come along.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 How often did you have meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, we used to have stew or something practically every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you keep a pig?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Where did she get the meat then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 From the butchers, the man \{ILLEGIBLE\} used to come round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 He used to call?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Was that foreign meat, or English meat, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Mostly English I'd have thought.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And did you have anything else in the way of rabbit or birds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Oh, yes, we used to have rabbit. Father used to shoot rabbits and catch them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you ever do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Oh, yes, plenty of times (laughter)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Trapping for rabbits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Anyhow, hit them on the head with a stick, catapult.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And then bring them home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Who used to skin them and prepare them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Mother, as far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And how were they cooked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, we used to have them in a pie, or stewed; baked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And do you remember what kind of meat you had besides - what was the stew made of? Beside rabbit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Beef.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you ever have pork or mutton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you have any kind of pudding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 We used to have steamed puddings, syrup puddings, or dumplings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you ever have any other kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Roly Poly or Spotted Dog.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you have puddings, though, that weren't sweet? You mentioned dumplings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And syrup puddings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes, but that was sweet, really. I mean pudding not as a dessert, not as a sweet course, but for a first course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 You didn't have Yorkshire pudding as a first course?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, Mother done it now and again, but not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And if your mother made dumplings would she serve them with the meat and vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 In the stew.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 She never served them first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And did you have a sweet often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No, very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 You usually didn't have syrup or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you ever have fresh fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Christmas time, that's about all,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you not have fruit trees in the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 We did have some fruit trees, apple trees.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Cooking or eating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 They was mostly eating apples.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 When did you eat them, the eating apples? Did you have them as part of a meal, or when?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No, generally used to take them, you know, just go and have one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you have breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes, not eggs and bacon, though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Could you tell me what you had for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Bread and dripping, toasted cheese.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you have anything in the way of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8717613\charrsid1594022 cereals}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 , or porridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 You said you never had eggs and bacon, did you never have part of an egg.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 I used to have an egg sometimes, Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 A whole egg?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes, sometimes when they was cheap, and I used to have a sausage when sausage come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 How often would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Sundays.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And what about anything else for breakfast, can you remember if there was anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did you ever have anything else on the bread besides dripping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Oh, a bit of butter now and again. Mostly bread and dripping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 What do you mean by now and again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Well, once or twice a week, perhaps, something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 You didn't have jam, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes, we used to have jam.
