\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 You don't remember thinking that she was very tired, or anything, when she was a boy?
