\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Did your mother have any help from neighbours or friends in her household work shopping?
