\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes. You never had 
so much a week in them days. They might have ... some people ... I mean, the well off farmers and that, they might have given their children pocket money, but none of the working class.
