\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes, I think his first station was west. I believe he went to Westerfield.
