\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And did he ever do agricultural work while you were still living at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Yes, at one time.
