\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 Were you a signalman all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5321501 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 I was a signalman and I finished up passenger guard at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Clacton{\*\xmlclose}
. That's how I finished up.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339059 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1264030\charrsid1594022 And your sisters who were domestic servants, did they ever have any other jobs.
